{"tid":1739530,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[愛國愛黨選前拉票][冧巴降]自發為心儀的候選人拉票","createTime":"2019-11-19T15:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T15:24:21.000Z","uid":99445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43bfd5c12274750faaf042ecaf942fff689e2e49","tid":1739530,"uid":99445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>離區議會只剩幾日,大家要為自己區既候選人拉票</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設我係「沙田市中心」既選民,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>「2號」候選人「鄧肇峰」</strong></span></span><br />\n依位<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>愛國愛黨</strong></span>既大好青年,當然要幫佢拉拉票<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">方法1:幫佢周圍貼，周圍派單張</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將佢既競選單張周圍貼，周圍派單張，特別係各位<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔太識字既老友記</strong></span>，一定要多多提醒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Lj0NA6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Lj0NA6.jpg&h=20c4e2ff&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千祈</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">千祈</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">唔好印錯佢個號碼</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老友記</span></span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">街坊</span></span></strong>一個唔小心投左俾另一位候選人就唔好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xLr6JbF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxLr6JbF.jpg&h=b7ee5aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>方法2:大大聲講俾身邊街坊,心儀候選人既號碼</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人類對<span style=\"color: red;\">數字</span>敏感,務求做到<span style=\"color: red;\">洗腦效果</span>,令街坊入到票站唔會搞錯<br />\n大聲叫「2號！！鄧肇峰！！」「記得投２號２號２號！！鄧肇峰！！」等洗腦口號<br />\n特別係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>選舉當日</strong></span>，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">票站附近</span></strong>，叫多點，大聲點<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ftu.org.hk/upload/news/2930/photo/5946355658a0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftu.org.hk%2Fupload%2Fnews%2F2930%2Fphoto%2F5946355658a0f.jpg&h=de73c32a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千祈</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">千祈</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">唔好叫錯佢個號碼</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如叫左做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「１號！！鄧肇峰！！」「記得投１號１號１號！！鄧肇峰！！」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://19ga.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/325363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F19ga.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F325363.jpg&h=448ec357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記住以上兩個方法，一旦搞錯號碼，都會變相幫另一位候選人增加選票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另一位候選人加上本身就支持既選民票數，會令另一位候選人票數增加，大大提升得票率<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">１１月２４日　區議會選舉，一票都不能少</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d164b53ea63820275299939d1b41a911e3aea7b2","tid":1739530,"uid":197121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"施法<br />\nMagic<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}